# Supabase Configuration
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# Instructions:
# 1. Create a new project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Go to Settings > API in your Supabase dashboard
# 3. Copy your project URL and anon key
# 4. Rename this file to .env
# 5. Replace the values above with your actual Supabase credentials
# 6. Run the SQL schema from src/lib/supabase.ts in your Supabase SQL editor

# For Production Email Notifications:
# 7. Sign up at https://resend.com and get an API key
# 8. Deploy the Edge Function: supabase functions deploy send-email
# 9. Set RESEND_API_KEY in your Supabase Edge Functions environment variables